<div id="share_header" class="box green_gray full_span">
  <h2>Coming Soon!</h2>
  <div id="interact_header_content" class="box_interior space_out">
    <p><%= link_to "Freecycle", freecycles_path %>. Free Downloads. Free Giveaways. And that is just for starters! </p>
    <p>Share your child's accomplishments. Think - one big, happy group blog where you can post your child's art, poetry, written articles, etc. Participate in themed contests. Motivate your student to do their best, and share with all of us. Everybody wins!</p>
